 <H1>Collections: MKCOL</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>The MKCOL method creates a new collection
</H2>
</UL><UL>
<LI><H2>MKCOL can be invoked with a request body
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>No request body: empty collection is created
<LI>Request body: media-type specific results
<UL>
<LI>primarily to reserve body for future capability
</UL></UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Benefits:
</H2>
<UL>
<LI>a simple method is used to create a collection
<LI>MKCOL method avoids problems with adding collection creation semantics to PUT</UL></UL></P>
